Enclosing class:
AssociationRules
public static class AssociationRules.Rule<Item> extends Object implements scala.Serializable
An association rule between sets of items. param: antecedent hypotheses of the rule. Java users should call javaAntecedent() instead. param: consequent conclusion of the rule. Java users should call javaConsequent() instead.
